{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"元素：focus 事件","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>focus</code></strong> 事件在元素获取焦点时触发。这个事件和 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\"><code>focusin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 最大的区别仅仅在于后者会事件冒泡。</p>\n<p><code>focus</code> 与 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"blur\"><code>blur</code></a> 正好相反。</p>\n<p>该事件不可取消，也不会冒泡。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在象 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> 这样的方法中使用事件名称或设置事件处理器属性。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'focus'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">onfocus</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件属性","title":"事件属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该接口还从其父级 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> 继承属性。</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"focusevent.relatedtarget_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FocusEvent/relatedTarget\"><code>FocusEvent.relatedTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a>，表示此事件的次要目标。在某些情况下（例如切换到当前标签页或离开当前标签页），处于安全原因，该属性可能会被设置为 <code>null</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"简单示例","title":"简单示例","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text input<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果\">结果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"简单示例 sample\" id=\"frame_简单示例\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event/_sample_.%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件委托","title":"事件委托","isH3":true,"content":"<p>此事件有两个可以实现事件委托的方法：通过在支持的浏览器上使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\"><code>focusin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 事件，或者通过设置 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> 的参数<code>useCapture</code> 值为 <code>true</code>。</p>\n<h4 id=\"html_2\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text input<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> form <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'form'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nform<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'focus'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'pink'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nform<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'blur'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果_2\">结果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"事件委托 sample\" id=\"frame_事件委托\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event/_sample_.%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%A7%94%E6%89%98.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#event-type-focus","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.Element.focus_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Element.focus_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>相关的事件：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"blur\"><code>blur</code></a>、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\"><code>focusin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focusout_event\" title=\"focusout\"><code>focusout</code></a></li>\n  <li>在 <code>Window</code> 目标上的该事件：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/focus_event\" title=\"focus\"><code>focus</code></a> 事件</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://javascript.info/focus-blur\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Focusing: focus/blur</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"事件属性","id":"事件属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"focus 事件在元素获取焦点时触发。这个事件和 focusin (en-US) 最大的区别仅仅在于后者会事件冒泡。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element: focus event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element: focus イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"focus","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/element/focus_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/element/focus_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc